{
  "message": "test(conformance): extend fuzz_pivot_table corpus with 20 edge-case seeds\n\nAdd structured binary seeds for pivot_table fuzz target:\n\nAggfunc coverage (10 seeds):\n- aggfunc_{sum,mean,count,min,max,prod,median,var,std,first}.bin\n\nEdge case coverage (10 seeds):\n- single_row: minimal 1-row frame\n- all_nulls: all null values (tests empty pivot output)\n- same_cell: all rows map to same row/col key\n- synth_mode_sum: synthetic mode generation\n- negative_vals: negative numeric values\n- float_vals: floating point values\n- mixed_nulls: null keys and values mixed\n- zeros: all zero values\n- max_rows_raw: 8 rows (raw mode max)\n- synth_max_rows: 8 rows (synth mode max)\n\nSeeds stored in fuzz/corpus/ and fixtures/adversarial/. All 23\npivot_table fixture tests pass.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
